      <title>加拿大央行将增加第二位外部人士进入利率制定委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/bank-of-canada-to-add-a-second-outsider-to-rate-setting-council</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆宣布计划重组加拿大央行的治理结构，在其主要决策机构中增加第二位外部人士，扩大参与制定利率的官员数量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/bank-of-canada-to-add-a-second-outsider-to-rate-setting-council</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 19:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
